    treatment: ['Treat underlying cause: chemotherapy for AL amyloidosis, tafamidis for ATTR amyloidosis, phlebotomy for hemochromatosis, enzyme replacement for Fabry', 'Diuretics for congestion (use cautiously - preload dependent)', 'Avoid beta-blockers and calcium channel blockers in amyloidosis (poorly tolerated)', 'Avoid digoxin in amyloidosis (binds to amyloid fibrils, toxicity risk)', 'Anticoagulation for AFib', 'Heart transplant for selected patients (avoid in AL with multi-organ involvement without hematologic remission)'],
