    emergencySigns: ['Fulminant myocarditis with cardiogenic shock', 'New sustained arrhythmia (VT/VF)', 'Rapidly declining heart function', 'Syncope in suspected myocarditis', 'Giant cell myocarditis (rapidly progressive)'],
