    emergencySigns: ['Acute limb ischemia (6 Ps: pain, pallor, pulselessness, paresthesia, paralysis, poikilothermia)', 'New rest pain', 'Non-healing wounds with infection/sepsis', 'Sudden worsening of claudication'],
